Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:35.34,OP Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(350,350)}I put my heart into blurry writing,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.59,0:02:41.09,OP Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(350,350)}but it will never reach you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:44.06,OP Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(350,350)}The letters dance in the heavens,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.51,0:02:52.52,OP Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(350,350)}stars of sad beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:58.61,OP Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(350,350)}I look at where I stand,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:04.28,OP Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(350,350)}and the ground shifts under me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:10.87,OP Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(350,350)}I am reminded now of when you extended
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:16.88,OP Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(350,350)}a helping hand to me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:24.47,OP Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(350,350)}I try to gather the glittering stardust around me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:30.44,OP Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(350,350)}but with fading thoughts, only my tears are certain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:36.07,OP Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(350,350)}I pressed my hand to my heart to fill the emptiness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:43.28,OP Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(350,350)}One day, our broken promise will link us all
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:35.34,OP Kan,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(350,350)}想い託す 揺れる文字は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.59,0:02:41.09,OP Kan,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(350,350)}あなたには 届かなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:44.06,OP Kan,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(350,350)}宇宙を舞い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.51,0:02:52.52,OP Kan,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(350,350)}星になる 光が切ないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:58.61,OP Kan,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(350,350)}踏み締めた足もと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:04.28,OP Kan,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(350,350)}揺らいでしまうから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:10.87,OP Kan,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(350,350)}手を伸ばしてくれた あの頃を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:16.88,OP Kan,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(350,350)}思い出してる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:24.47,OP Kan,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(350,350)}キラリ 星屑たち 集めてみても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:30.44,OP Kan,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(350,350)}涙 ぽろぽろぽろ こぼれて 消え入りそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:36.07,OP Kan,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(350,350)}ぎゅっと 指の隙間 胸にあてたの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:43.28,OP Kan,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(350,350)}いつか 砕け散った約束を リングに変える
Dialogue: 1,0:27:17.61,0:27:30.38,ED Kan,,0,0,0,,{\blur 2\fad(250,250)}目を覚ましたとき いつもの癖で“おはよう”
Dialogue: 1,0:27:31.04,0:27:43.76,ED Kan,,0,0,0,,{\blur 2\fad(250,250)}あと何度 同じ泣きそうな顔させるの?
Dialogue: 1,0:27:46.85,0:27:57.32,ED Kan,,0,0,0,,{\blur 2\fad(250,250)}その運命は まるで蛍火のように見えた
Dialogue: 1,0:27:59.53,0:28:12.13,ED Kan,,0,0,0,,{\blur 2\fad(250,250)}風を泳ぐように 心を揺らすよ
Dialogue: 1,0:28:16.50,0:28:25.47,ED Kan,,0,0,0,,{\blur 2\fad(250,250)}何度も 何度も 問いかけても
Dialogue: 1,0:28:25.76,0:28:32.90,ED Kan,,0,0,0,,{\blur 2\fad(250,250)}鏡に写る日々は 答えくれない
Dialogue: 1,0:28:33.27,0:28:42.66,ED Kan,,0,0,0,,{\blur 2\fad(250,250)}いつかは 消えた未来もう一度
Dialogue: 1,0:28:43.11,0:28:49.00,ED Kan,,0,0,0,,{\blur 2\fad(250,250)}信じたまま。。。
Dialogue: 1,0:27:17.61,0:27:30.38,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur 2\fad(250,250)}When I awoke, you greeted me with the usual "Good morning"
Dialogue: 1,0:27:31.04,0:27:43.76,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur 2\fad(250,250)}I've put you through so much and wonder how long it will persist
Dialogue: 1,0:27:46.85,0:27:57.32,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur 2\fad(250,250)}Our fate seemed like the light of fireflies to me
Dialogue: 1,0:27:59.53,0:28:12.13,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur 2\fad(250,250)}It fluttered on the wind and shook my heart
Dialogue: 1,0:28:16.50,0:28:25.47,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur 2\fad(250,250)}No matter how often I ask,
Dialogue: 1,0:28:25.76,0:28:32.90,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur 2\fad(250,250)}the lives in the mirror give no answer
Dialogue: 1,0:28:33.27,0:28:42.66,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur 2\fad(250,250)}One day, I will have faith
Dialogue: 1,0:28:43.11,0:28:49.00,ED Eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur 2\fad(250,250)}that I have a future yet
